tool_description: An API showing audiobooks of all game of thrones books
title: Game of Thrones Audio Book

api_list.name: Get all game of thrones audiobooks of a specific book
api_list.description: Get all game of thrones audiobooks of a specific book
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://game-of-thrones-audio-book.p.rapidapi.com/books/{bookid}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "game-of-thrones-audio-book.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
